00:39:28,300 --> 00:39:29,710
No...

516
00:39:30,770 --> 00:39:32,600
I will protect her.

517
00:39:37,870 --> 00:39:40,650
So please don't bother us.

518
00:39:41,800 --> 00:39:45,420
I'm sure you understand since you have a girl you want to marry.

519
00:39:47,510 --> 00:39:51,450
If she is very precious to you...

520
00:39:51,450 --> 00:39:54,510
Kotoko is very precious to me.

521
00:40:01,150 --> 00:40:04,180
I can't stand looking at Kotoko

522
00:40:04,180 --> 00:40:06,370
suffer so much.

523
00:40:14,280 --> 00:40:16,270
What do you say?

524
00:40:28,310 --> 00:40:32,860
Irie-kun, please say "Kotoko loves me"

525
00:40:32,860 --> 00:40:35,660
You used to say that.

526
00:40:36,980 --> 00:40:38,760
Please.

527
00:40:45,330 --> 00:40:47,990
Do whatever you want.

528
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:56,010
Sure.

529
00:40:56,010 --> 00:40:58,770
I will do whatever I want like you said.

530
00:40:58,770 --> 00:41:02,540
So don't meddle anymore, got it?

531
00:41:02,540 --> 00:41:05,820
This is a promise between men!

532
00:42:37,710 --> 00:42:42,460
This time... is it really the end?

533
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:48,290
Do I have to give up on Irie-kun?

534
00:42:48,290 --> 00:42:50,750
It's impossible.

535
00:43:14,660 --> 00:43:16,430
Brother...

536
00:43:28,900 --> 00:43:33,150
Are you really going to marry the woman
you had the arranged marriage meeting with?

537
00:43:34,590 --> 00:43:36,350
What is it all of a sudden?

538
00:43:36,350 --> 00:43:38,400
Please answer me.

539
00:43:40,450 --> 00:43:43,960
It's probably going to happen.

540
00:43:44,730 --> 00:43:49,040
Do you really love her?

541
00:43:52,220 --> 00:43:53,960
What is going on, Yuki?

542
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:56,770
Please answer my question.

543
00:43:58,400 --> 00:44:01,830
Because...

544
00:44:01,830 --> 00:44:04,770
Because the person you love is...

545
00:44:05,870 --> 00:44:08,640
Kotoko, right?

546
00:44:17,520 --> 00:44:22,440
Because in the hospital room, you gave Kotoko...

547
00:44:23,080 --> 00:44:23,590
a kiss - - -
-Next time...

548
00:44:23,590 --> 00:44:27,250
I will introduce you to Sahoko-san.

549
00:44:27,940 --> 00:44:31,520
She is beautiful and she is supposed
to be good at cooking.

550
00:44:33,250 --> 00:44:36,000
I'm sure you will like her.

551
00:44:37,330 --> 00:44:40,060
She is a good match for me.

552
00:44:43,400 --> 00:44:47,930
I'm sure everything will work out...

553
00:45:16,950 --> 00:45:18,960
Good morning, Kotoko.

554
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:21,340
Oh, good morning, Kin-chan.

555
00:45:21,340 --> 00:45:23,310
Are you going to work at the cafeteria?

556
00:45:23,310 --> 00:45:25,170
Yeah.

557
00:45:25,170 --> 00:45:27,110
Today's lunch special is...

558
00:45:27,110 --> 00:45:29,710
chicken cutlet.
You like it, right?

559
00:45:29,710 --> 00:45:32,070
I will give you an extra portion in secret.

560
00:45:32,070 --> 00:45:33,360
So you have to come and eat.

561
00:45:33,360 --> 00:45:35,850
Okay, thank you.

562
00:45:40,100 --> 00:45:42,250
Hey...

563
00:45:42,250 --> 00:45:45,950
Next Sunday...

564
00:45:45,950 --> 00:45:48,830
If you have time...

565
00:45:48,830 --> 00:45:51,030
Do you want to go out with me?

566
00:45:52,390 --> 00:45:54,340
Oh, well...

567
00:45:54,340 --> 00:45:56,680
I got tickets for a movie from a customer at Aihara.

568
00:45:56,680 --> 00:45:58,810
I thought you might enjoy it for a change.

569
00:45:58,810 --> 00:46:02,880
Uh... it's an action movie... you will feel exhilarated.

570
00:46:06,460 --> 00:46:08,570
After all, you don't want to go out
with just two of us, right?

571
00:46:08,570 --> 00:46:10,500
- Sure.
- How about Jinko - - -

572
00:46:11,110 --> 00:46:13,060
What?

573
00:46:13,060 --> 00:46:16,160
Sure. Let's go, just the two of us.

574
00:46:17,970 --> 00:46:20,480
Uh, this means...

575
00:46:20,480 --> 00:46:23,680
It's a date. Are you sure?

576
00:46:23,680 --> 00:46:28,960
You helped me a lot with Mr. irie.

577
00:46:29,970 --> 00:46:33,360
I want to thank you, so let's go on a date.

578
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:36,920
Okay.

579
00:46:36,920 --> 00:46:39,780
Well, see you later then.

580
00:46:46,750 --> 00:46:48,500
Alright!

581
00:47:04,250 --> 00:47:07,080
I was told that the president will be
discharged from the hospital next week.

582
00:47:07,080 --> 00:47:08,720
Congratulations.

583
00:47:08,720 --> 00:47:10,770
Thank you very much.

