587
00:47:24,670 --> 00:47:27,300
That's fine with me.

588
00:47:28,250 --> 00:47:30,840
I appreciate your help.

589
00:47:31,830 --> 00:47:34,700
Thank you very much, Naoki-san.

590
00:47:34,700 --> 00:47:39,950
Chairman Oizumi promised us an
amount of financial support.

591
00:47:39,950 --> 00:47:43,110
Now our company is safe.

